<HEAD>Nazi Hunter Expelled From Algeria</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PARIS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Nazi hunter Beate Klarsfeld, who went to Algeria
planning to demonstrate at the Arab summit in a call for recognition
of Israel, said Tuesday she was interrogated by Algerian police and
