<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The U.S. dollar moved lower in early trading
Wednesday against the Japanese yen, and prices fell on the Tokyo
Stock Exchange.
   The dollar opened at 125.27 yen, down 0.50 yen from Tuesday's
close of 125.77 yen.
   On the Tokyo Stock Exchange, the Nikkei Stock Average of 225
